  "detailed_description": "Top Burger is an exciting fast food simulation game. You just opened a burger restaurant, let's see if you can put together burgers fast enough to satisfy your ever growing number of customers!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe game also comes with many achievements and a \"create your burger\" mode which lets you build super high burgers, taking advantage of all the unlocked items.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGame Features:<br />\r\n- More than 150 levels<br />\r\n- Hours of gameplay<br />\r\n- Three game modes<br />\r\n- Dozens of types to deliver to your customers",
